<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>قُلْتُ قَدْ وَقَعَ فِي قَلْبِي مِنْهَا شَيْءٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَقَالَ قَالَ ابْنُ مَسْعُودٍ الْإِثْمُ حَوَّازُ الْقُلُوبِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قُلْتُ إِنَّمَا هَذَا عَلَى الْمُشَاوَرَةِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قَالَ أَيُّ شَيْءٍ يَقَعُ فِي قَلْبِكَ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قُلْتُ قَدِ اضْطَرَبَ عَلَيَّ قَلْبِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>قَالَ الْإِثْمُ حَوَّازُ الْقُلُوبِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>